Install and setup:
Install the checkstyle plugin https://checkstyle.org/eclipse-cs/#!/ (drag and drop the Install button into Eclipse)
Window -> Preferences -> Checkstyle -> New -> Type: External -> Select /build/checkstyle.xml -> Set it as default once its added
Window -> Preferences -> Java -> Code Style -> Clean Up -> Import /build/style/eclipse/cleanup.xml
Window -> Preferences -> Java -> Code Style -> Formatter -> Import /build/style/eclipse/eclipse_style.xml
Window -> Preferences -> Java -> Code Style -> Organize Imports -> Import /build/style/eclipse/eclipse.importorder

Usage:
Add checkstyle view: Window -> Show View -> Other -> Checkstyle/Checkstyle violations
To check a file or module: right click on it -> Checkstyle -> Check code with checkstyle